# Documentation Issue

Please open documentation issues that are not specifically for documentation within the
PowerShell/PowerShell repository in the [PowerShell Docs](https://github.com/MicrosoftDocs/PowerShell-Docs/issues) repository.

On this [doc page](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/powershell/module/microsoft.powershell.core/export-modulemember?view=powershell-6), description for example 5 mentioned `Get-Test` but `New-Test` is actually in the codes
title: Documentation Issue: should be New-Test instead of Get-Test
